A review of the genus Xistra Bolivar 1887 (Orthoptera: Tetrigidae) with description of two new speciesThe genus Xistra Bolivar, 1887 is reviewed. An original key is given for all 15 known species of the genus. Two new species, X. klinnema sp. nov. and X. wuyishanensis sp. nov., are described from China. The holotypes of the new species are deposited in the Institute of Zoology, Shaanxi Normal University.